    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事随着每次探索而进展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《创世纪日志》讲述了主角 Ruina 和她的辅助机器人 Nekoro 的故事以及他们的过去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事从两个角度展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过去和现在发生了什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鲁伊娜和涅科罗继续寻找解决人类面临的危机的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/b6c361623142abacaecb795cfd743103.poster.avif?t=1761102910\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/b6c361623142abacaecb795cfd743103.webm?t=1761102910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/b6c361623142abacaecb795cfd743103.mp4?t=1761102910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-行动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高速动作射击游戏，以高速移动并瞄准地板、墙壁和天花板。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用两种类型的武器：阿尔法武器和贝塔武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它需要资源管理并相应地安排攻击时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的战斗风格可以根据强化物品的组合而发生巨大变化！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好准备迎接强大的敌人并制定策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/fa4f81be445b1bd4cf541c0c49ec8421.poster.avif?t=1761102910\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/fa4f81be445b1bd4cf541c0c49ec8421.webm?t=1761102910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/fa4f81be445b1bd4cf541c0c49ec8421.mp4?t=1761102910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-收集物品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索过程中可以获得各种强化物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你探索归来时它们就会迷路，但它们都拥有强大的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用探索结束时获得的物品来解锁新装备！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到你自己的最佳构造！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道具种类有……嗯……超过200种……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/2b8a3bc32d2a0f358f29fde969731fbb.poster.avif?t=1761102910\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/2b8a3bc32d2a0f358f29fde969731fbb.webm?t=1761102910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155590/extras/2b8a3bc32d2a0f358f29fde969731fbb.mp4?t=1761102910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-挑战BOSS战和困难内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地区都有强大的敌人等待着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以在设置中更改难度级别，因此这绝对是一个令人满意的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Boss Rush中挑战分数排名！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 相较于移动版本进行了重大改进和调整</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于 Steam 版本，我们纳入了最初想要的难度级别和功能，并添加了系统并以各种方式进行了平衡调整，包括难度设置功能，以便即使是已经广泛玩过智能手机版本的玩家也可以以新的方式享受游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整个游戏进展顺利，您现在可以获得解锁和强化事物所需的许多代币，从而使整个游戏过程中的收集变得顺畅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在高难度设置的后半部分，BOSS 会有新的极其强大的攻击方式，所以可能需要多次重试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难度级别可以随时从标题屏幕更改，因此请随意尝试一下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-分发指南</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 只要您遵守基本的道德规则，您可以自由发布此游戏的视频和直播，包括货币化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・无需提前联系我们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・如果您能附加您的商店页面（本页的 URL），我们将非常感激。</p>",
